To compile simple.c:
 gcc -o simple `pkg-config --cflags players` simple.c `pkg-config --libs
 playerc`

(or more easily)
    make simple

To run simple:
 player simple.cfg (in one window)
 ./simple (in another window)


To compile example0.cc:
    g++ `pkg-config --cflags playerc++` -g    example0.cc  `pkg-config --libs playerc++` -o example0

(or more easily)
    make example0

To run example0:
 player simple.cfg (in one window)
 ./example0


